Big Brother (Clement2022) 13-Jul-20 01:19 PM
I, representing The New Order would like to give our honest condolences to the residents of New Porto in this trying times. I believe the Federal Government should provide more relief in disasters like this and declare a national emergency- a "War against Tsunamis". With the funds received, we want to plan and build a new, affordable, more disaster resistant housing with our Senate Economic Advisory Board. We will send surveyors to calculate the cost of this project and design it and will contract the building rights to the lowest bidder, in an attempt to save the taxpayers money. Moreover, we will also build a larger dock and create opportunities for tourism, an industry very popular and lucrative in many developing countries. These infrastructure projects, moreover, ALSO employs the people who lost their work from the disaster, combatting the unemployment issue too. We also plan to create a Federal agency, the Federal Reserve, to plan the "war against Tsunami" and allocate resources to those most vulnerable to the disaster as well as administer the construction of hospitals and schools, creating something similar to the New Deal where we plan to build infrastructure and schools in order to decrease unemployment further. However, the government will offer extra subsidies for the affordable housing to citizens affected by the disaster in order to house them so they can rebuild their lives. We can introduce a similar thing here in patrium, to encourage long-term de-radicallisation. this will ensure that we can peacefully co-exist with one another and that we can ensure that we shall have peaceful-coexistance long term. no other bill offers long term stability, rather just ffocusing on the short term.
Fourthly, Safety among private buisnesses. While private buisnesses do a decent job at keeping their workers safe, i beleive that the government ought to step in to help with the safety of their workplaces, and protect the worker. one of tthe reasons we likely have communist rebellions is due to the fact that working conditions overall took a drastic fall ever since timothy miller, the staunchest advocate for workers rights among private industries, was attacked by our nation to seize his assets. ever since then, buisnesses have become more and more hostile to workers in order to not be seized by the patriann government. Public Safety Act, 2020 Introduced by Sen. Mega (FSL) Whereas Patrium has been gripped by terror and violence; Be the following enacted by the Senate of Patrium: SECTION 1: SUMMARY This Act will empower law enforcement to act quicker on terrorism and other violent crimes by...

Sen. Esat T. Erdagi 09-Feb-21 10:43 AM
Imagine for a moment, that you have a lung cancer
That is a terrible situation of course, and you would want it be rid of
So, what do you do to cure yourself?
You go to a hospital, get chemotherapy and radiotherapy
Get surgeries
To remove the cancer from your body
You want to root it out
One of the symptoms of lung cancer is coughing, severely
And what happens if you only take a cough drop and do not treat the cancer itself
The disease kills you
We must treat the causes, not the symptoms.
3
